OL,5, The BBC committed "significant         
OL,6, editorial failings" in its reporting of
OL,7, an antisemitic attack on Jewish        
OL,8, students, Ofcom has found.             
OL,10,FThe media watchdog observed that the   
OL,11,FBBC failed to follow its editorial     
OL,12,Fguidelines on due impartiality and due 
OL,13,Faccuracy in a 2022 online article.     
OL,15,FA separate BBC London news broadcast on
OL,16,Fthe same story did not breach due      
OL,17,Fimpartiality or accuracy rules.        
OL,19,FHowever, Ofcom said the BBC had made a 
OL,20,Fserious editorial misjudgement.        
